{"tid":599273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作困擾不開心　男租客酒店浴室燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-03-20T09:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T01:06:00.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d414953fd6c2076597565445e526f0312d58171","tid":599273,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/mobile/bkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180320%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html&d=ZhIX5m104SAY8N8dsYFrA7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e3dfabfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180320/mobile/bkn-20180320132533150-0320_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n油麻地男子酒店燒炭亡。今午(20日)12時許，吳松街92號一間酒店，職員發現一名男租客逾時仍未退房，好奇下遂拍門查看，惟良久沒有回應，同時聞到房內傳出燒焦味，擔心租客發生危險下，遂報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方聯同消防接報趕至，發現男子昏迷倒臥酒店浴室，身旁有一堆炭灰，經檢驗後證實已經死亡。警方初步調查後，相信事件無可疑，正聯絡其親友處理後事。 <br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者年約50歲，本地人，入住酒店時已攜燒炭用的工具，並留有遺書，疑因工作問題不開心尋死。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350"},{"pid":"84351f674ff553c9748dc4f376490797298c92c7","tid":599273,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"自殺呢啲家常便飯既小事都當新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57ecb2a07ff1c76f6d0a573b3f4df5c24dad8e7","tid":599273,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:58:50.000Z","msg":"疑因工作問題不開心尋死。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905697a380c53d2f7860a6aa4a1971bfda6024e6","tid":599273,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:03:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔捱得，廢老</span></span>"},{"pid":"b985f99152136aa699cefb8f4b136f6011eeffb4","tid":599273,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:05:38.000Z","msg":"死還死唔好阻人搵食啦<br />\n間房仲點租出去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54309b5974c0a88438fa43d4708f73c2cc4d5e4a","tid":599273,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b985f99152136aa699cefb8f4b136f6011eeffb4","tid":599273,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:05:38.000Z","msg":"死還死唔好阻人搵食啦<br />\n間房仲點租出去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T01:06:00.000Z","msg":"照租出去，你擔心住果個算啦"}]}